text: Ni$ illa i kunwi umedya ucbie di Iboahim akked wid illan yides, mi nnan i ugdud nnsen: "nemgirred ikwen, kunwi akked wayen teppanzem, war Oebbi. Nenkeo ikwen. Taadawt akked dd$el, ersen d garane$, i lebda, alamma tumnem s Oebbi Yiwen". Kkes ed awalen i inna Iboahim, i baba s: "ad velbe$ a ppeppusemmeev, xas ur iyi Ikellef Oebbi, fellak, s wacemma". A Mass nne$! Ppkal nne$ fellaK; nutub iK; $uoeK tu$alin
